dsDescriptionValue.value: This catalog compiles and cross references the accessions in the world's major Centrosema collections at ClAT, ILCA, CSIRO. EMBRAPA-CENARGEN, and AREC Fort Pierce-University of Florida. It is a colIaborative effort by the curators of these collections under !he coordination of Dr. Ruiner Schultze•Kraft  of CIAT. IBPGR is pleased to join with CIAT in the publication of this catalog.

publicationCitation.value: SCHULTZE-KRAFT, R.; Williams, R.J.; Coradin, L.; LAZIER, J.R.; KRETSCHMER JUNIOR, A.E. 1989. 1989 World catalog of Centrosema germplasm = Catálogo mundial 1989 de germoplasma de Centrosema. Centro Internacional de Agricultura Tropical (CIAT); International Board for Plant Genetic Resources (IBPGR), Cali, CO. 322 p.
